episodes.title: Australia's Satanic Cult claims a victim | Listen To This
episodes.description:
An apparent kidnap by a Satanic cult keeps Charley and Jack guessing, with the case where everything is not exactly as it first seems.

Will you be able to solve the real crime mystery at home before they solve it on screen? Join true crime creator Charley Bourne and comedy influencer Jack Taylor as they open up a shocking new crime file and root through the twists and unpack the details from the comfort of their sofa. (Series 1 episode 2)
